snippet.title: Ishido: The way of stones (PC MS-DOS, 1990)
snippet.description:
Gameplay of "Ishido: The Way of Stones", a puzzle video game released in 1990 by Accolade and developed by Publishing International.

Emulator: DOSBox-X 0.83.1
